Rewards Platform is the module run on the Sweet Tooth engine in our production SaaS offering of the Sweet Tooth engine.

INSTALL
=======

1. Install magento enterprise
1.1. git clone git@wdca.unfuddle.com:wdca/enterprise-sampledata.git
1.2. git clone git@wdca.unfuddle.com:wdca/me11110.git
1.3. Create me11110 database and import enterprise-sampledata/enterprise-sampledata.php.sql
1.4. Run the magento installer.

2. Run dev/shell/install.sh

3. Install dependent modules - all have dev/shell/install.sh
3.1. git clone git@wdca.unfuddle.com:wdca/mmst.git
3.1.1. git checkout rewardsplatform
3.2. git clone git@wdca.unfuddle.com:wdca/rewardsloyalty.git
3.3. git clone git@wdca.unfuddle.com:wdca/tbtcommon.git
3.4. git clone git@wdca.unfuddle.com:wdca/recurly.git

4. Note: For a production environment, disable symlinks, which are being enabled in the upgrade script.

